  <heading>BRKN</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Propagate break to next partition</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction propagates break to next partition. If the Last active element of the first source predicate is false, then
the destination predicate is set to all-false.
Otherwise, the destination and second source predicates are left unchanged. This instruction does not set the condition flags.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>True</predicated>
  </desc>
